productsInfo.productDetails:
Featuring a purple base floor length anarkali in raw silk with gold and velvet applique work. 
It comes along with gold cape with floral jaal work and purple churidaar. 
FIT: Fitted at bust. 
COMPOSITION: Raw silk, lace. 
CARE: Dryclean only.

Presenting a striking kurta in bold green embellished with elaborate resham embroidery on the yoke and along the sleeves. Team it with a pair of brown jeggings and nude pumps to make a chic style statement.

productsInfo.productDetails:
Featuring an indigo high-collared flared anarkali in chanderi embellished with golden geometric patterns and gold hemline. 
It has long sleeves and front button placket. 
It is paired with matching voile churidaar and indigo net dupatta with gold border all around it. 
FIT:Cut for relaxed fit. 
COMPOSITION: Chanderi, voile, net. Lining: Voile. 
CARE: Dryclean only.
